{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- I think at the time he found out about the International Red Cross in Geneva, and ask me to write a note, which I did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we got responded, this name is registered, is alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's alive, but they're in Irkutsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- but I-- Daddy, matter of fact, taught me how to speak, how to write in Russian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All I remember the P is R.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, that's what he-- and then we try to send him packages as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a horrible experience for them as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then for-- we ask for pictures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my brother-- that's why we asked, made the picture during the beginning, in the beginning of the '40s.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we sent them the picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I hated it, but now I like it, because that's the only thing I-- it brings back close to mine-- to our home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how he remained there until the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Meantime, I being home, Daddy came back and start to-- when they give us the concession, they said that's not enough.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The people have to work for the Germans in order to stay home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is safer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Meantime I was in hiding here and there, and then one night I was also-- my sister slept in another place, and I was-- we had like a [INAUDIBLE] had storage, like an outside in the backyard special storage, for certain things, for cold, whatever.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So Mom tried to hide me, and covered up, and sit all night through to watch me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the Germans, because they came during-- the Nazis, because they came unexpected during the night, wherever they expected Jews, wherever area they knew that Jews are, look there.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
